Riki -- High-DPS, starting stats 4 int, 15 agi, 4 str, base speed 280, base damage 3, Stats Gain per level 0.30 int, 0.30 str, 1.00 agi
starting item Weak Dagger increase damage by 2 and give 3 attackspeed base attack time 1.40

LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1
increase Riki Pure Evasion by 5% and his health by 125
Riki will gain 1% normal Evasion for every 4 agility up to 35% from agility max and for every 1% evasion riki got, he gain 0.6% max
health bonus

talent 2
Increase Riki agility by 10 and his damage by 8
Any items use that deal damage, Riki will add 100% of his attack damage to that item and having 20% more damage with items use as well
and all of riki spell will deal 35% of his agility into bonus damage as well.

PASSIVE F OR D Thief Soul
increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF riki will gain 3 life per agility point he also gets 40% increase agility for a total of his intelligence and strenght he also got
a special dagger that cannot be change at all and he can use 1 more other dagger with it, he also got 5% Pure Evasion that can Evade
basic attack and spell and he start with 70 more health and 12 attack speed as well
DEBUFF riki only gain 2 life per strenght and he take 90% more damage from pure,magical,physical also he can only use dagger weapons type
he also lose 35% of his max mana and spell vamp wont have any effect on riki spell lost and any pure damage type will do 2.5% of riki health
as damage bonus and he cannot have any Critical chance and Critical damage at all only from Roktoru dagger

Roktoru Dagger Special
increase base damage by 2 increase by 1 for every 3 level
increase attack speed by 8 increase by 1 for every 2 level
Physical spell crit chance 10% increase by 1% for every 10 level
Physical spell crit damage 120% increase by 1% for every 2 level
can also be use to deal 100% crit for a 1 time use with any spell of riki spell having 15% more crit damage as well
cooldown of 70 second

talent level 25 upgrade Thief Soul
add a new modifier Death to the Weaks
every attacks will do 0.7% of the target current health in damage and spell will do 0.5% of their max health in damage, Enemys below
50% health will take 40% increase damage from Riki spell that does damage and if their are below 18% health they will take 125% increase
damage from riki spells and attacks as well, also increase his pure resist by 35% and also reduce his magical damage output by 10%


