add a new modifier Poison Dagger
after striking the enemy,they will get poison dealing 11 plus 18% of agility in pure damage per 0.5 second and disabling regeneration
for 3, also increase the damage they take by riki spell by 15% and if their die under the effect of the poison, they will spread it
to other target for 50% increase damage and lasting 2 more second and can also spread again and those will spread, also making it spread
to infinity but those that spread from the Second poison that spread will only have 0.5 duration increase.

