PASSIVE D OR F BackStab -NOTE- this affect only work behind that mean if riki attack from the front once the target 2 stacks
increase riki agility and his attack speed, Riki will deal bonus damage behind his target base on his Agility, each time he strike
that target in his back, he will reduce their armor every time up to 7 8 9 10 stack of reduce armor to them, at max stack the enemys
will take Pure damage from Riki basic attacks and be stun for 1 seconds, Enemys cannot be stun again for 15 seconds.

Agility bonus 8% 12% 16% 20%
